# ── Cleanup policy: markdown allowlist only ─────────────────────────
# Ignore all markdown except explicitly allowlisted files.
# NOTE: new docs under docs/ must be added to this allowlist.
*.md
!/AGENTS.md
!/README.md
!/CLAUDE.md
!/GEMINI.md
!/SECURITY.md
!/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md
!/.zig-bootstrap/README.md
