!/docs/STRUCTURE.md
!/docs/PATTERNS.md
!/docs/ABI_WDBX_ARCHITECTURE.md
!/docs/ZIG_MACOS_LINKER_RESEARCH.md
!/docs/plans/*.md
!/docs/api/*.md
!/docs/guides/*.md
!/benchmarks/README.md
!/benchmarks/STRUCTURE.md
!/examples/README.md
!/tasks/todo.md
!/tasks/cleanup.md
!/tasks/lessons.md

